00:46:21.510 --> 00:46:23.180
So problem with
CIGS is if you're

00:46:23.180 --> 00:46:25.280
looking for
Earth-abundant films,

00:46:25.280 --> 00:46:28.010
again if we want to scale-- if
we want solar energy to scale

00:46:28.010 --> 00:46:30.530
to terawatt levels, if
we want it to provide all

00:46:30.530 --> 00:46:32.450
of human energy
needs-- then we're

00:46:32.450 --> 00:46:34.360
going to need to use
elements and materials

00:46:34.360 --> 00:46:37.430
that are Earth-abundant, cheap
to find, cheap to produce,

00:46:37.430 --> 00:46:39.660
and CIGS isn't going
