looks at in yellow,

00:47:46.300 --> 00:47:48.800
this is what you
could get if you

00:47:48.800 --> 00:47:54.010
look at annual production of
that semiconductor material

00:47:54.010 --> 00:47:56.360
now in terms of what is
being produced to produce

00:47:56.360 --> 00:47:58.140
the raw materials that make it.

00:47:58.140 --> 00:48:00.610
And then the known
economic reserves,

00:48:00.610 --> 00:48:03.840
what can we mine and
get economically today,

00:48:03.840 --> 00:48:05.220
how much could it produce?

00:48:05.220 --> 00:48:07.990
And your worldwide
consumption is on this line,

00:48:07.990 --> 00:48:11.280
