00:48:11.280 --> 00:48:13.590
And the ones of note
for this discussion

00:48:13.590 --> 00:48:16.320
are Cad-tel, CIGS, which
is slightly better,

00:48:16.320 --> 00:48:19.430
and then CZTS, which is
rather plentiful even

00:48:19.430 --> 00:48:23.057
with reserves that are
currently being mined now,

00:48:23.057 --> 00:48:24.890
